{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55409, "create_time": 1647819753, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "更何况有很多翻译者本身就已经肉身翻墙了，这样做无疑加剧对华人群体的种族歧视，对他们自己来说也没什么好处啊？", "timestamp": 1647819753}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55411, "create_time": 1647819928, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re : 还包括墙内对乌克兰局势的言论", "timestamp": 1647819928}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55414, "create_time": 1647820758, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "“有人在诋毁我们”\n”他们做了什么”\n“他们把我们说过的话翻译了一遍”", "timestamp": 1647820758}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55417, "create_time": 1647821201, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 2, "text": "[tmp]\n一群舔洋人舔惯了的慕洋犬习惯性的给洋人递刀子罢了，不过话说回来现在洋人算个寄吧？洋人怎么看我们又有什么寄吧用？最后总还是要杀光的。", "timestamp": 1647821201}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55420, "create_time": 1647821767, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "最起码让墙外这些人看到墙内的邪恶, 不无辜，不值得可怜 。毕竟墙外大多数国家和人反华的也只是反政府，不是中国人。而国内绝大多数网民不仅反对其他国家，还反对其人民，甚至在战争、天灾等面前幸灾乐祸，恨不得对方被毁灭，心理极度阴暗，最起码作为人的同情心都没有。然而在国内由于这种声音是“主旋律”，反对者没办法发出声音（被封号、限制、被扣帽子），官方当婊子还立牌坊，只能去外网发。让全世界看看这些", "timestamp": 1647821767}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55421, "create_time": 1647821879, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "再说了，只是翻译而已。他们在怕什么？", "timestamp": 1647821879}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55422, "create_time": 1647822107, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 4, "text": "[tmp]\n蛆虫的小圈子活动罢了，不用关注。\n可以卑微如尘土，不可扭曲如蛆虫", "timestamp": 1647822107}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55425, "create_time": 1647822415, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 4, "text": "[tmp]\n即使生于臭水沟也要学会仰望星空，而有些蛆虫总是热衷于把臭水沟里的粪水挖出来给别人看", "timestamp": 1647822415}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55426, "create_time": 1647822547, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 4, "text": "[tmp]\n如果非要说什么心理的话就是逆向民族主义，通过诋毁自己的民族以显得自己相比同类有优越感，小反贼是这样的", "timestamp": 1647822547}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55427, "create_time": 1647822733, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re : 反之同理", "timestamp": 1647822733}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55430, "create_time": 1647822826, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Carol: 幸灾乐祸怕是东亚圈的共性，不至于这么舔墙外", "timestamp": 1647822826}, {"author_title": "nmslese", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55445, "create_time": 1647824484, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 6, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Carol: 赶紧肉身翻墙去当黄皮肥皂的原料😅", "timestamp": 1647824484}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55460, "create_time": 1647826001, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 我甚至根本没有在说什么诋毁不诋毁的事情。我只是在质疑这样的行为对同样作为华人群体的翻译者本身并没有好处但是有实质性的坏处", "timestamp": 1647826001}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55461, "create_time": 1647826043, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 因此我不理解这些翻译者的行为的目的及合理性，", "timestamp": 1647826043}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55463, "create_time": 1647826411, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 看到了，然后呢？这些翻译者相当一部分肉身在墙外，外国人发现了中国人的邪恶，由此引发的对中国人的歧视或仇恨难道不是将他们这些肉身在墙外的华人作为首当其冲的目标吗？", "timestamp": 1647826411}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55465, "create_time": 1647826539, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 墙内会因此改变什么吗？墙外华人的生活环境难道会变得更好吗？", "timestamp": 1647826539}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55466, "create_time": 1647826736, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 还有一部分翻译者是现在在墙内但是希望将来肉身翻墙的，他们难道希望将来面对一个对华人群体更加敌视的环境吗？", "timestamp": 1647826736}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55468, "create_time": 1647827113, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 当墙外对墙内舆论建立了这样的刻板印象后，这些翻译者难道能指望墙外人在现实中把他们和墙内人区分开吗？", "timestamp": 1647827113}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55469, "create_time": 1647827167, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "所以我完全不能理解这样一场“运动”究竟对哪个群体有利", "timestamp": 1647827167}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55475, "create_time": 1647828020, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "如果你不提这一茬，我都不知道现在有大翻译啥啥...", "timestamp": 1647828020}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55476, "create_time": 1647828162, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Grace: 可以参见维基相关词条", "timestamp": 1647828162}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55477, "create_time": 1647828595, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "有没有可能 参与该运动的人并不是中国人", "timestamp": 1647828595}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55479, "create_time": 1647828738, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 9, "text": "[tmp]\n让世界看清中国人的愚昧、自大、恶臭…\n让那些在海外离岸爱国两头讨好的人被迫割席一边", "timestamp": 1647828738}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55482, "create_time": 1647828871, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 9, "text": "[tmp]\n外国人总以为中国政府才是不好的\n无非是想告诉他们，这种印象早就过时了", "timestamp": 1647828871}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55521, "create_time": 1647831349, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "墙外华人把这些言论翻译出去，以为能让墙内人感到羞愧，能让外国人一起对抗中国，实则是他们想多了。墙内人早就不在意外国人的看法了，不仅不在意，而且还看不起。", "timestamp": 1647831349}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55954, "create_time": 1647873334, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "Re 洞主: 一种可能是这些人把反中当宗教信仰了，纯粹为了反中而反中没点脑子也不考虑下自身利害关系", "timestamp": 1647873334}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 55963, "create_time": 1647873515, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "至于为什么把反中当信仰，可能跟敌对势力在舆论战场上的有组织行动有关", "timestamp": 1647873515}], "create_time": 1647819675, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1647873515, "likenum": 12, "n_attentions": 12, "n_comments": 27, "pid": 20328, "poll": null, "reply": 27, "text": "挺想知道主动搞大翻译运动的人是什么想法。那些言论确实没啥素质(例如b站对于日本地震新闻的弹幕)，但是翻译传播到外国舆论空间上后必然导致对中国人的仇视提高。这些翻译者难道觉得将来出国遇到外国人(如乌克兰、日本人等)时对方会把他和其他中国人区分开么？", "timestamp": 1647819675}}